# k8s-man-lb

**Author:** lukesh-b  
**Repository Status:** Work in Progress  


## Core Areas

- Multi-node cluster configuration
- Deployment and rollout strategies
- Load balancing and service exposure
- Resource management and scaling
- Infrastructure structuring
- Git workflow management with branches, merges, and release tagging

## Repository Structure

- `architecture/` – Cluster and networking design documents
- `infrastructure/` – Namespaces, storage, and cluster setup
- `workloads/` – Reusable Kubernetes manifests for pods, deployments, services, ingress, config
- `projects/` – Real-world deployment projects
- `scripts/` – Automation scripts for setup, deployment, and scaling
- `.github/workflows/` – CI/CD workflow definitions

## Work in Progress

This repository is under continuous development to expand Kubernetes deployments and infrastructure automation patterns. Tags, branches, and commits are maintained to track progress and milestones.

